ActTougher Penalties for Child Predators Act
SubjectOrder Fixing December 31, 2024 as the Day on Which Section 29 of the Tougher Penalties for Child Predators Act Comes into Force
PrecisOrder fixing December 31, 2024, as the day on which section 29 of the TOUGHER PENALTIES FOR CHILD PREDATORS ACT, chapter 23 of the Statutes of Canada, 2015, COME INTO FORCE in order to enact the High Risk Child Sex Offender Database Act.
